  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-SI-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package declares ed25519 as the signing algorithm and carries a valid SHA-256 content hash, but the signature value itself has been omitted, rendering structural integrity unverifiable (W-SI-01). All 13 credibility factors are populated and the decision record records an Accepted outcome consistent with a completed assessment cycle.",
