      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; formal change-control process in place.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver is version-controlled and basic regression tests exist, but the test suite does not cover non-Newtonian shear-stress regimes critical for hemolysis prediction. Change-control documentation is incomplete. Achieved level 2 falls short of required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
